          <title>Flyers fire coach John Tortorella in midst of another losing season</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The Philadelphia Flyers fired coach John Tortorella on Thursday with nine games left in another losing season for a franchise that hasn’t been in the playoffs since 2020. The Flyers are last in the Metropolitan Division at 28-36-9 for 65 points under the notoriously brusque Tortorella.]]></description>
